{
  "stem": "25831.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She had studied photography before she got married for maybe three or four months.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it was enough to make her a pretty good photographer.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my father had inherited a business from my grandfather whose name was Jakob Ollendorff.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And Jakob Ollendorff lived in Kattowitz-- Kattowitz, which is in Upper Silesia, which after World War I became Polish, was called Katowice.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But before World War I already, my grandfather had moved his main office to Breslau.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He had an interest in a couple of coal mines, not a majority interest.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was just a little interest.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But that little interest enabled him to buy, to become a coal distributor.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he sold coal by the carloads to industries.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I-- I remember later on when there was a coal strike and when miners struck in England, my grandfather, of course, was dead by the time.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My father had an enormous amount of business because people would buy coal, you know, from wherever they could scrape it up.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But now coming back to my house-- yeah, my grandfather had a wife.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Her name was Jenny Ollendorff, who was one of I think 11 or 13 children, I'm not quite sure.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he, my grandfather, had been a consul or vice-consul for Bolivia, I believe.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I remember photographs and pictures when I went to my grandmother's house which showed my grandfather's house displaying the German flag and the Bolivian flag on certain holidays.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My father worked very hard.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He went to his office six days a week.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he did come home for lunch, which was really the dinner.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He always came around 1:45.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We ate for half an hour.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Then he took a 15 minute nap.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then he went back to work.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
